Dialogue: 9,0:00:01.11,0:00:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Que diabos aconteceu lá?!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:03.24,0:00:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Não foi uma escolha consciente ou algo assim...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles são maiores que os meus.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:08.62,0:00:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Então, as pessoas intersexuais se adaptam\Ndependendo do parceiro escolhido.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Se você escolheu ser mulher,\Nit significa que você encontrou um homem!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou saindo!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Parabéns!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho um deck com cogumelos!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:20.76,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos jogar quando sairmos!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:24.38,0:00:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Não jogo cartas com você!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:30.47,0:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Me pergunto se a nave-colônia\Nconseguiu retornar para Sidonia.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:34.23,0:00:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Sidonia ainda existe.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:36.77,0:00:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Planeta Sete, segundo satélite, \Bbase principal, falando.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:39.65,0:00:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nave de transporte, responda.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:41.69,0:00:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Podemos ouvir você claramente.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:42.78,0:00:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}Este lugar é basicamente um paraíso—
Dialogue: 9,0:00:46.41,0:00:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:49.37,0:00:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Base principal, falando do navio de transporte!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:55.71,0:00:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos uma emergência!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}{\r}Gauna—
