Dialogue: 9,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,O que vai acontecer com a Killy na próxima?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que todos estamos torcendo por ele.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:31.41,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Coloque esse feixe nessa seção aqui.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:33.96,0:03:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi perto.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou bater em você.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:48.14,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Empurre um pouco mais.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aproveitando a chamada!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ren!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe muito!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Tanikaze[T2]...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gardes não voam como você.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninguém se feriu,
Dialogue: 9,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,mas você realmente precisa ser mais cuidadoso.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}, Ok, sim...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:28.01,0:04:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos, vire essa cara para cima.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá, ajudar.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Tanikaze[T0].
Dialogue: 9,0:04:35.31,0:04:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Como você soube como me sentia?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora você está surpreso.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Você nunca percebeu?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:42.06,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso ver como você se sente\Npelo seu rosto.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:48.15,0:04:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso te alegrou?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Não me olhe!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Agradeço ao céu que finalmente terminamos de mudar.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:02.38,0:05:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambos temos estado bastante ocupados.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou ansioso para cozinhar isso.{is this ingredients or cooking ware?}{ingredients}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza de que a receita de stews da minha Avó será ótima.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou ansioso também.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Casa querida, casa.[T0]
Dialogue: 9,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, olá!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu, Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuhata[T0]!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles voltaram!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:23.48,0:05:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aguarde!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuhata está aqui?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda não pode subir.{kyyhz}{ayy}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, fique lá embaixo.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está me enganando, certo?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor![T2]
Dialogue: 9,0:05:43.04,0:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana!{**-san}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!{**-san}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,De verdade?[T2]
Dialogue: 9,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,O que meu equipamento está fazendo\Nfora no corredor?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Bem...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu terminei, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:54.30,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fique aí.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos por aqui.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:01.14,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,É o quê?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode abrir os olhos agora.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:06.52,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Me maravilio com o que poderia ser.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dá!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Muito legal!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma mesa aquecida!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyama{**-san} me deu!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:19.95,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu me familiarizei bastante com eles.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:22.71,0:06:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Minha pergunta é: por que todo o conteúdo do meu quarto foi substituído por um?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:28.67,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Este é o único quarto com tatames de palha.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:30.76,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Existem muitos quartos vazios para você.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:34.01,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, e por sinal, eu me estabeleci no quarto ao lado do Tanikaze{**-san}.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:38.85,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Devíamos estar economizando energia após os danos sofridos no outro dia.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:44.94,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Por isso também me mudei aqui.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana[T0]!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode tirar com uma mão só!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare de brincar, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:20.26,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não é minha babá, Yuhata{**-san}.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Já se acostumou com os próteses?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, um pouco.[T1]
Dialogue: 9,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo, então.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:36.07,0:07:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos testar seus novos controles com dez dedos.{pictured: prototype PS4 controller by madcatz}
Dialogue: 9,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Os cérebros humanos são incríveis.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:54.88,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Às vezes sinto que nasci com dez dedos na mão.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:59.39,0:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tente se conectar ao controlador.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:03.22,0:08:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
