Dialogue: 9,0:17:20.74,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, certo.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Minha participação nisso\Ndeve ser mantida em segredo.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Também da Izana.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Se alguém descobrir, verei essa missão como um fracasso.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Voltando...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:35.17,0:17:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo de volta.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo de volta.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está errado?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Você parece ter visto um fantasma.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou bem.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:43.51,0:17:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,De verdade.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:45.56,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,E a Izana?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Na sua sala.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:54.06,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:55.57,0:17:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso conversar com você?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente tenho que fazer isso!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:05.99,0:18:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:10.62,0:18:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,E então?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Um...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Podemos conversar aqui dentro?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:15.96,0:18:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Qualquer outro pedido?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma missão secreta de alto nível?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:22.97,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho que investigar o Vila Milenar amanhã.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:27.14,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,O que?!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:27.64,0:18:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A Vila Mil Anos?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:28.97,0:18:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Você sabe disso?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Está entre as Dez Primeiras Atrações da Sidonia.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:35.69,0:18:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas... Temos que estar de volta ao local de construção amanhã.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe com isso.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:40.65,0:18:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Podemos tirar amanhã e o dia seguinte de folga.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,O dia seguinte será suficiente?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:46.12,0:18:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Não estava certo se conseguiríamos arrumar acomodações o rápido o suficiente.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:50.91,0:18:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A-acomodações?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:55.13,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode simplesmente me dizer\Nse você está me convidando para férias.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso não são férias!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou完全自动化助手：以下是翻译：
Dialogue: 9,0:19:05.22,0:19:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,O dia seguinte será suficiente?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajuda-me com minha tarefa!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,O que te pegou, Nagate?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:13.27,0:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso tudo é um pouco repentino.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Merda...
Dialogue: 9,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não estou acostumado a isso.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:24.45,0:19:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que você não quer passar a\Na noite em algum lugar decadente.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:35.00,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,De fato?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Agradeço ao céu!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:38.54,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo?!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:39.42,0:19:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Izana!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:48.55,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanikaze{**-san} convidou Izana{**-san}\Não é um passeio de uma noite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:55.94,VillageSign,,0,0,0,,[T0]Senshukyo
Dialogue: 9,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Para o Vila Mil Anos!{\i0}
Dialogue: 9,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:02.69,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Você acordou cedo, né?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:07.78,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nada!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado pelo alimento!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:15.41,0:20:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:17.12,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu me esqueci completamente!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu deveria estar me encontrando com minha vovó!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmo um cego poderia ver através das suas mentiras.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou bastante chocado.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}{\r}Hmm...
Dialogue: 9,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Devemos chegar no horário.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nessa direção, né?
