Dialogue: 9,0:21:07.92,0:21:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso aqui é o acesso, não é?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou bastante animado.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos em missão, Izana.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:17.18,VillageSign,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\c&H626464&\blur1.05\frz358.3\fax-0.2\pos(1008,465)}Vila do Milênio
Dialogue: 9,0:21:13.51,0:21:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,De acordo.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meu Deus.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Então isso é...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,a Vila do Milênio.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Nagate!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:54.43,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,É ainda mais impressionante de perto!
Dialogue: 9,0:22:05.02,0:22:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate?
Dialogue: 9,0:22:06.90,0:22:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu... Izana.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Nagate...
