Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:35.39,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se este mundo estiver condenado à ruína,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:35.39,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se esta é a minha sentença de morte,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:38.89,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se a minha vida for sacrificada,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:38.89,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então eu me lançarei
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:44.48,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que eu deveria viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:44.48,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que devo crer para viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:50.15,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:50.15,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sem ter te conhecido
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:53.57,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}nunca sentiria dor assim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:53.57,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}com essa dor que aperta o peito
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:23:00.16,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}arrancando meu coração em pedaços
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:23:00.16,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por não conhecer a dor antes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:02.91,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}É um requiem primitivo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:02.91,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}no horizonte do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:04.37,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ecoando até
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:04.37,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o fim da noite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:08.21,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}os limites do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:08.21,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}requiem inexprimível
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:10.13,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}E mesmo agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:10.13,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e ainda
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:11.84,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}em este mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:11.84,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}buscando
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:15.26,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu busco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:15.26,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}algo diferente desde agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.26,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por ti
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.26,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que te dizia
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:20.89,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu me lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:20.89,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}também do contentamento que encontrei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.60,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o prazer em te encontrar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.60,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mesmo o frio de sua ausência
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:28.82,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e a passagem da sua presença
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:28.82,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}estou lembrando tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:31.90,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:31.90,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque eu te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:35.66,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Gelo cresce no meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:35.66,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e o mapa do mar que se desvia com as lágrimas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:39.37,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por cima das feridas dentro de mim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:39.37,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mesmo as feridas que ficam no interior também
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:43.75,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu levarei tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:43.75,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}vou carregar tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:50.75,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e seguir meu caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:50.75,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}vou percorrer esta estrada
